      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEALTAINE (5) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at her last four runs. Last time finished 2nd on April 20 over 480m at this track behind Aero Buster beaten a head (29.37) in an A10. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Overdue and gets her chance. DARVER SPARK (3) recorded a 1.5 lengths third in an A9 last time 29.51 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Leading player again. PAS DALY (1) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.2 lengths (29.46) behind Aero Buster at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. TEWMAX AUSSIE (2) claimed an A9 win two back before missing the frame at his latest appearance in an A9 at this track over 480m (30.13). No surprise to see him back in winning form.",
